com.blukii.sdk.config

Class SmartBeacon.OnConnectionListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blukii.sdk.config.Blukii.OnConnectionListener
      • com.blukii.sdk.config.SmartBeacon.OnConnectionListener
  • Enclosing class:
    SmartBeacon

    public abstract static class SmartBeacon.OnConnectionListener
extends Blukii.OnConnectionListener

    Abstract class for callbacks of SmartBeacon specific requests.

    The callbacks are additionally provided to the callbacks of base class Blukii.OnConnectionListener.
